snippet.title: What is Fractured Online?
snippet.description:
The Closed Beta is coming on April 6, 2022!
The CEO of Dynamight Studios, Jacopo Pietro Gallelli is here to explain in 14 minutes what Fractured Online is and what makes it unique. Discover core features, gameplay, races and a lot more!

Share with your friends, an amazing adventure awaits you in Fractured Online!
Get all the information you need to jump into Closed Beta: 👇
https://bit.ly/ClosedBetaStartsSoon

⚔️ Get Fractured Online today: https://fracturedonline.com
🌐 Stay connected through social media: https://linktr.ee/FracturedOnline
🔔 Subscribe to YouTube. Stay up to date with our latest news!
